15
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:58,920
He didn't die from diabetes.

16
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:06,760
Zhang Dajiang.

17
00:02:07,600 --> 00:02:08,759
Zhang Dajiang.

18
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:10,600
Zhang Dajiang.

19
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,320
Zhang Dajiang.

20
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:13,680
Him?

21
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:18,079
He was an acrobat when he was alive.

22
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:20,000
After he got this disease,

23
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:22,730
