37
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:51,200
But the deceased had given up.

38
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:54,680
Every day he lived was agony.

39
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:58,320
He couldn't even kill himself.

40
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:00,760
Lanlan.

41
00:03:01,120 --> 00:03:02,640
Is it possible that

42
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:05,320
Mom was very sick,

43
00:03:05,320 --> 00:03:07,160
and wouldn't take her medicine properly,

44
00:03:07,160 --> 00:03:09,240
