around 20 years old.

294
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:23,770
Judging by her clothes,

295
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:25,560
she was likely a student.

296
00:16:25,680 --> 00:16:26,520
On the deceased's abdomen,

297
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:27,800
there is a sutured wound

298
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:30,440
about 20 centimeters long.

299
00:16:31,280 --> 00:16:32,760
But the incision is uneven.

300
00:16:32,760 --> 00:16:34,920
The retraction of the wound edges

301
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:37,880
indicates she was cut before death.

302
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:40,120
But the suturing is very sloppy.

303
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:41,640
And the material used

304
00:16:41,640 --> 00:16:43,760
isn't professional surgical thread.

305
00:16:43,760 --> 00:16:45,040
You mean

306
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,680
while the deceased was still alive,

307
00:16:46,680 --> 00:16:47,640
she was cut open?

308
00:16:49,760 --> 00:16:50,760
It's very likely.

309
00:16:52,280 --> 00:16:54,400
To be so cruel to a young girl,

310
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:56,040
what a beast.

311
00:17:00,360 --> 00:17:04,160
I once heard a foreign patrolman say

312
00:17:04,560 --> 00:17:05,490
that in England,

313
00:17:06,319 --> 00:17:08,400
there was a heinous criminal

314
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:10,839
called Jack the Ripper.

315
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:14,760
He brutally persecuted many women,

316
00:17:15,079 --> 00:17:17,200
slicing their stomachs open

317
00:17:18,040 --> 00:17:20,240
and leaving their organs exposed.

318
00:17:20,839 --> 00:17:22,400
It was absolutely terrifying.

319
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:24,079
No one has caught him to this day,

320
00:17:24,079 --> 00:17:25,480
and no one knows who he is.

321
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:27,960
Could this Jack the Ripper

322
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:29,220
have come to Shanghai?

323
00:17:57,560 --> 00:17:58,360
What's wrong?

324
00:17:59,360 --> 00:18:01,220
The victim's stomach is missing.

325
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:03,730
The stomach is gone?

326
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:07,720
Can you determine the time of death?

327
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:10,400
The corneas are completely cloudy,

328
00:18:10,920 --> 00:18:13,320
but the livor mortis blanches on pressure.

329
00:18:13,800 --> 00:18:15,240
The time of death

330
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:17,720
should be last night,

331
00:18:17,880 --> 00:18:20,080
between 10:30 and 11:30.

332
00:18:21,880 --> 00:18:24,080
Why was it Comprador Zhou's gift

333
00:18:24,080 --> 00:18:26,040
that was swapped for a female corpse?

334
00:18:26,040 --> 00:18:27,440
Did he offend someone?

335
00:18:27,680 --> 00:18:29,840
Or is someone trying to frame him?

336
00:18:36,840 --> 00:18:37,960
The soil is fine,

337
00:18:38,360 --> 00:18:39,360
and dark.

338
00:18:40,120 --> 00:18:41,720
It's from deep underground.

339
00:18:42,080 --> 00:18:43,640
The body was buried before.

340
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,000
That doesn't make sense.

341
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:47,840
If the killer wanted to frame Comprador Zhou,

342
00:18:47,840 --> 00:18:49,440
why go to such lengths

343
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:50,980
after killing him,

344
00:18:51,080 --> 00:18:52,140
burying him first,

345
00:18:52,520 --> 00:18:54,720
and then digging him up to move the body?

346
00:18:55,120 --> 00:18:57,760
Maybe Comprador Zhou killed him

347
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,440
and buried the body.

348
00:18:59,960 --> 00:19:01,840
But someone else found it,

349
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:03,360
dug it up,

350
00:19:03,360 --> 00:19:04,960
and swapped it with his gift.

351
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:06,080
That means,

352
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:08,880
the killer and the person who moved the body

353
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,330
aren't the same person.

354
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:19,480
There's something inside the clothes.

355
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:20,680
Receipt.

356
00:19:20,960 --> 00:19:23,840
Sanhe Hotel,

357
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:25,480
on Jiyun Road.

358
00:19:26,720 --> 00:19:27,450
Brother Bao.

359
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:28,600
Get someone to check

360
00:19:28,600 --> 00:19:30,480
the guest list of Sanhe Hotel.

361
00:19:30,920 --> 00:19:31,440
Also,

362
00:19:31,680 --> 00:19:32,440
check the nearby girls' school

363
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:33,320
to see if anyone

364
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:36,040
matches the deceased's characteristics.

365
00:19:37,160 --> 00:19:37,960
Okay.
